item.dc:creator: totaltheme
item.content:encoded: Total is the best thing that has ever happened to my small business. They helped me offer great coverage to all my employees at an affordable price, saving me time & money.

item.title: Great People
item.dc:creator: totaltheme
item.content:encoded: Finding a great healthcare plan wasn't at the top of my list, but Total made finding and choosing the right plan for me a piece of cake. I'm so glad I found them.

item.title: Superb
item.dc:creator: totaltheme
item.content:encoded: Great options, great people, great prices. Best health insurance ever. Period.

item.title: Cool
